#### Things to know

- Use gRPC port 19530 for SDK connections (pymilvus, Java, Go, Node.js)
- HTTP port 9091 is for health checks and RESTful API (limited functionality)
- LoadBalancer IPs (external gRPC) are for access from outside the cluster only
- Each environment is isolated -- collections in pai-dev are not visible in pai-test/prod
- Milvus stores vector data in MinIO automatically -- do not modify `milvus-bucket`

